OL,3,CMayor Sadiq Khan criticises
OL,4,C'disappointing' spending review
OL,6,FSir Sadiq Khan has described the
OL,7,FGovernment's failure to fund new
OL,8,Ftransport projects in London as
OL,9,F"disappointing".
OL,11,FThe mayor of London pledged to
OL,12,F"continue to fight for the investment
OL,13,Fwe need" as he said there must never
OL,14,Fbe an attempt to "level down London".
