OL,3,CMayor Sadiq Khan criticises
OL,4,C'disappointing' spending review
OL,6,FSir Sadiq is frustrated that
OL,7,FChancellor Rachel Reeves did not use
OL,8,Fher spending review to support
OL,9,Fproposed projects such as the
OL,10,Fextension to the Docklands Light
OL,11,FRailway (DLR) and the Bakerloo Tube
OL,12,Fline.
OL,14,FHe did welcome the decision to provide
OL,15,FTransport for London (TfL) with a long-
OL,16,Fterm funding settlement, which it has
OL,17,Fsought for a number of years.
OL,19,FThis set out #2.2 billion in capital
OL,20,Ffunding over four years.
