OL,3,CMayor Sadiq Khan criticises
OL,4,C'disappointing' spending review
OL,6,FSir Sadiq said: "It's ...
OL,7,Fdisappointing that there is no
OL,8,Fcommitment today from the Treasury to
OL,9,Finvest in the new infrastructure
OL,10,FLondon needs.
OL,12,F"Projects such as extending the
OL,13,FDocklands Light Railway not only
OL,14,Fdeliver economic growth across the
OL,15,Fcountry, but also tens of thousands of
OL,16,Fnew affordable homes and jobs for
OL,17,FLondoners.
