OL,3,CMayor Sadiq Khan criticises
OL,4,C'disappointing' spending review
OL,6,F"Unless the Government invests in
OL,7,Finfrastructure like this in our
OL,8,Fcapital, we will not be able to build
OL,9,Fthe numbers of new affordable homes
OL,10,FLondoners need.
OL,12,F"As mayor, I'll continue to make the
OL,13,Fcase to the Government that we must
OL,14,Fwork together for the benefit of our
OL,15,Fcapital and the whole country.
OL,17,F"The way to level up other regions
OL,18,Fwill never be to level down London.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
