OL,3,CMayor Sadiq Khan criticises
OL,4,C'disappointing' spending review
OL,6,F"I'll continue to fight for the
OL,7,Finvestment we need so that we can
OL,8,Fcontinue building a fairer, safer and
OL,9,Fgreener London for everyone."
OL,11,FAndy Lord, London's transport
OL,12,Fcommissioner, said the funding
OL,13,Fsettlement means TfL can complete the
OL,14,Fintroduction of new trains on the
OL,15,FPiccadilly Tube line and DLR, and new
OL,16,Fsignalling on 40% of the Tube network.
